## 3. 插件规范

### 3.1 标准目录结构

插件应打包为 `.zip` 或遵循以下目录结构：

```text
my_plugin/
├── plugin.yaml          # 插件元数据 (核心)
├── src/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   └── main.py          # 入口代码
├── requirements.txt     # Python 依赖
├── config_schema.json   # 配置项 Schema (JSON Schema)
├── assets/              # 图标、本地化文件
└── tests/               # 单元测试
```

### 3.2 `plugin.yaml` 元数据示例

```yaml
name: weather_expert
version: 1.2.0
description: 天气查询专家插件
author: "Author Name"
license: MIT

# 扩展点声明
extensions:
  - type: tool
    entry: src.main:query_weather
  - type: event_listener
    events: ["user.connected"]

# 权限声明
permissions:
  - network.outbound: "https://api.weather.com/*"
  - memory.read: true

# 依赖
requires:
  python: ">=3.11"
  packages:
    - requests>=2.28
```

